CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 10, 1962, pg. 17, reads: "AT NAACP MEET - Surprise visitors to the recent Young Adult meeting of the National Association for the Advancement of Colored People, at the Loendi Club, were Henry Musamali (fourth from left) of Uganda, East Africa, and Peter Kanari, of Kenya, East Africa... - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of three women, and five men, including Henry Musamali second from left, and Peter Kanari fifth from left, posed behind table with food, possibly for NAACP Young Adult meeting, another version
